{"tid":230582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個覺得好有緣份既經歷","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T03:54:45.000Z","uid":54377,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f0e7c9bb96e2510ab4d4299b8786adc86660b0","tid":230582,"uid":54377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:42:32.000Z","msg":"之前係高登同個巴打因學業問題pm交流過一段時間<br />\n佢有比佢電話比我 但我冇加佢 <br />\n所以得我有佢電話 佢冇我電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次返炒散 同個同事傾開計覺得好熟咁 好似個位巴打 <br />\n岩傾之下交換左電話 點知真係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5424b4ac7ce0d4b9f34f80388db83d5852c301e","tid":230582,"uid":20811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:47:35.000Z","msg":"1月1。倒數完，出去尖沙咀揾我細佬，嗰時仲未有smartphone ，se機年代，但又打唔通send 唔到message ,諗住到時瘋狂打俾佢，點知一出到尖沙咀地鐵站係人群中間撞到佢。"},{"pid":"486f51041aa4948e7e5e75fd0351ee8393254807","tid":230582,"uid":58736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"細個打機識到個人 住隔離座<br />\n仲有聯絡 識左接近十年啦<br />\n係一位好兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd2eadab1c2d03f899368c4d8d502b17c90d0e3","tid":230582,"uid":106126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:11:21.000Z","msg":"以前一班人去機鋪打機打灣岸<br />\n我係後面睇 我個frd 同隔離個男仔一齊打得好開心<br />\n我走去搵問個男仔係咪識我個frd<br />\n佢話唔識我frd 但係識得我<br />\n原來係以前補習啲同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ca2d0ad681db0ee170b42c2e8e6adacc55d05b","tid":230582,"uid":50784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"上forum買野，點知原來佢係我中學師兄，<br />\n大家仲要好啱傾，佢係我曾經最鍾意既一個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cea75f9a74002545c65e7ffaef29fda999e05aa","tid":230582,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"係連登因為好複雜好複雜好複雜嘅事識到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0917752efff84f2e64746f997c58f1b9c7abf2","tid":230582,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011068a10e19fbcc2771843d5e79ad0fff0ee268","tid":230582,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"大家係差唔多既時間失戀，旅行散心<br />\n<br />\n旅行期間相遇，到噯昧，到相戀，到long D, 不斷既聚散，到分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好似發咗場夢咁，大家都好愛好愛，但再愛都無辦法一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家大家都有另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝佢永遠幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a967bd5f9baa50a7cd0db1ff94d49e4122a4572","tid":230582,"uid":21924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"有次去圖書館求撚其借本書<br />\n點知排我後面條友又係借同一本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed0df6846adcc4d9c1b8d5021c1c9087dc3e094","tid":230582,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"以前成日搭巴士會見到一個女仔<br />\n因為佢好靚女所以我特別留意佢<br />\n幾乎每晚搭果架巴士都會撞到<br />\n後來我因為有D事就唔洗再搭<br />\n之後亦都無再見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後未我番一份炒散<br />\n識到另一個女仔<br />\n果個女仔話佢有個朋友咁同佢講<br />\n［你ig po果個男仔咁似我以前搭車撞到果個既］<br />\n我即刻諗起佢<br />\n然後佢俾佢個朋友既相我睇<br />\n原來真係佢！<br />\n原來佢都記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時有D機會要珍惜  那怕係偶遇<br />\n只要勇敢D可能會有意想不到既驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f94e96fc396db3c77f59945e2796136351d8218","tid":230582,"uid":109786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"好細個落公園玩滑板車 識左個都係玩緊滑板車既女仔<br />\n之後升小一開學個日 咁岩就見到佢 原來同我讀同一間小學<br />\n但佢去到小二就轉校 <br />\n我地都冇再聯絡<br />\n結果前兩年 有個frd問我係咪識呢個女仔 佢話佢識我 想問我個frd拎我電話<br />\n一睇相之下 原來就係佢"},{"pid":"b9ef51e316c9a058a2a4b56a35d06f1df3212514","tid":230582,"uid":56141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"App識左個男仔 <br />\n本身知asso大學同一間<br />\n識左傾落先知原來同小學都同校 師兄黎<br />\n細個又住同區勁近 <br />\n中意啲野又好似 <br />\n就好似一直有一個人同我平行空間一齊生活緊 <br />\n直至之前係app茫茫人海都遇到<br />\n我地都覺得好神奇咁都識到 <br />\n然後做左男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d696ff0e625b0d2a503adae2a33a865e95a1273","tid":230582,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}